  "What is a radical?": "什么是激进?",
  "An expression that uses a root symbol (√) to indicate a root of a number": "使用根符号( {}) 表示数字根的表达式",
  "Any expression with an exponent": "带有引号的任意表达式",
  "A fraction with variables": "带有变量的分数",
  "A number that is always irrational": "一个总是不合理的数字",
  "A radical is a mathematical expression that uses a root symbol (√) to indicate a root of a number. The most common radical is the square root, but cube roots and higher roots are also radicals.": "激进是一个数学表达式,它使用根符号()来表示数字的根。 最常见的激进是平方根,但立方根和高根也是激进。",
  "What is a radicand?": "什么是射线?",
  "The number or expression under the radical symbol": "激进符号下的数字或表达式",
  "The answer after simplifying a radical": "简化激进派之后的答案",
  "The small number written above the radical": "写在激进主义之上的少数数字",
  "The coefficient in front of the radical": "激进分子面前的系数",
  "The radicand is the number or expression inside the radical symbol. For example, in √50, the radicand is 50. Simplifying means extracting perfect square factors from the radicand.": "弧线是激进符号中的数字或表达方式。 例如,在 50 中, 弧线是 50 。 简化意味着从弧线中提取完全的正方形系数 。",
  "What is a perfect square?": "什么是完美的广场?",
  "A number divisible by 4": "A 数除以 4",
