  "A number with exactly two factors": "具有确切两个因素的数字",
  "Any even number": "偶数数字",
  "A perfect square is a number that is the square of a whole number, such as 1, 4, 9, 16, 25, 36, 49, 64, 81, 100. Its square root is an integer.": "一个完美的正方是一个数字,是一个整数的正方形,例如1,4,9,16,25,36,49,64,81,100。",
  "What does 'simplest radical form' mean?": "\"最简单的激进形式\"是什么意思?",
  "The radicand is a prime number": "半径是一个质数",
  "The radical equals a whole number": "激进分子等于一个整数",
  "No perfect square factors remain under the radical and no radicals appear in any denominator": "激进下没有任何完全的平方因素存在,也没有任何极端因素出现",
  "The radical has been converted to a decimal": "基数已转换为小数点",
  "A radical is in simplest form when the radicand has no perfect square factors (other than 1) and there are no radicals in any denominator. Both conditions must be satisfied.": "激进主义最简单的形式是,当射线线没有完全的平方因素(除了1个)和任何分母中都没有激进分子的时候。 两种条件都必须得到满足。",
  "What does 'rationalize the denominator' mean?": "\"合理分母\"是什么意思?",
  "Move the radical from the denominator to the numerator": "将激进分子从分母移动到分子",
  "Remove the radical from the denominator by multiplying numerator and denominator by an appropriate radical": "通过将分子和分母乘以适当的激进分子,将激进分子从分母中除去",
  "Simplify the numerator only": "仅简化分子",
  "Convert the fraction to a decimal": "将分数转换为小数点",
  "Rationalizing the denominator means eliminating any radical from the denominator of a fraction by multiplying both the numerator and denominator by the appropriate radical expression.": "分母合理化意味着通过将分子和分母乘以适当的激进表达式来消除分母分母的任何激进。",
  "What is the product property of radicals?": "激进分子的产品财产是什么?",
