  "√(a + b) = √a + √b": "(a+b) = a + b",
  "√(a · b) = a · √b": "________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________",
  "The product property of radicals states that √(a · b) = √a · √b when a and b are non-negative. This property is fundamental for simplifying radicals by breaking the radicand into factors.": "激进分子的产物产值表示,当a和b为非负值时,(a □ b) = a □ b □ b,这一产物对通过将辐射分解成各种因素来简化基质具有根本意义。",
  "What is the quotient property of radicals?": "激进分子的商数属性是什么?",
  "√(a/b) = (√a)(√b)": "□(a/b)=(a)(b)",
  "√(a/b) = √a − √b": "(a/b) = a-b",
  "√(a/b) = √a / √b for a ≥ 0 and b > 0": "(a/b) = a / b = 0 和 b > 0",
  "√(a/b) = a/√b": "__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________",
