  "The square root of a number n is a value that, when multiplied by itself, equals n. For example, √25 = 5 because 5 × 5 = 25. The principal square root is always non-negative.": "数字 n 的平方根是一个数值,当乘以本身时,等于 n。例如, ' 25 = 5,因为 5 × 5 = 25. 主平方根总是非负的。",
